# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   It makes pyenv switch to the right version automatically.
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different OSs or Python versions,
#   Pipfile.lock might have conflicts.
#  Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is generally recommended to be tracked.
#  poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock is generally recommended to be tracked.
#  pdm.lock

